# MelodyVerse Authentication App

This project implements a login and signup functionality for a fictional music streaming service called "MelodyVerse". It uses Node.js, Express, React, and JWT for authentication.

## Features

- User Registration and Login
- JWT-based Authentication
- Protected Routes
- Responsive Design with Tailwind CSS
- Form Validation with Formik and Yup

## Requirements

- Node.js and npm
- MongoDB (or your preferred database)

## Setup Instructions

### Backend

1. Clone the repository and navigate to the backend directory:
   ```bash
   git clone <repository-url>
   cd backend

